	</h1>
	<p class="intro-p">
		Being a founder means being a <span>generalist</span>. If you're launching a tech-startup, you need to have an intimate understanding of how your product functions. This means getting your hands dirty with both the <span>code</span> and the <span>design</span>.
	</p>
